item.title: Can someone help me with
item.dc:creator: @runefreak10 runefreak10
item.description:
@runefreak10 wrote:

[quote=“newb pk3r, post:3, topic:261521”][quote author=primadude link=topic=345343.msg2662716#msg2662716 date=1234310107]

can someone help me with spawning an portal?

i went to

public void NewObjects

now what?

Add this into it:

makeGlobalObject(objectX, objectY, objectID, face, 10);

Replace ‘objectX’ with the X coordinate of where you want the object to be spawned.
Replace ‘objectY’ with the Y coordinate of where you want the object to be spawned.
Replace ‘objectID’ with the ID of the object you want to spawn.
Replace ‘face’ with the integer of which way you want the object to be facing (-3, -2, -1, 0).
[/quote]

how do i make a new portal code?[/quote]

Do you have one already?

Read full topic
